      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains structurally flawless with a documented subframe reinforcement and a fully serviced Double-VANOS system. Suspension kinematics are factory-crisp, utilizing the original M-tuned MacPherson front and multi-link rear setup. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with zero oxidation. A mechanically transparent, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
